title: The 5 Steps To Building A Social Circle In A New City From Scratch (Ep 253)
description:
LINKS:

Get coached by Robbie to build your social circle - https://www.innerconfidence.com/community

SHOW NOTES:

02:03 - If I drop you in a new city to start a new  social-circle, how would you go about this? - Find out here! 

06:07 - Tip the bouncers and bartenders! Why? - Find out here!

**

25:30 - Position yourself as a VIP promoter - Learn here!

47:31 - "I don't give a ** about your girls" - How to handle these tough situations when entering cool places!
